Assembling a Team
In every conversation I=E2=80=99ve had with Uri, Chris and the Clear Street=
=E2=80=99s leaders, one thing that comes up over and over again is the impo=
rtance of building the right team.=C2=A0
This is something that practically every founder will tell you: the team is=
