9c-8a81c7c9746d?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8=
ExkRNpU ], BlackRock CEO Larry Fink said, =E2=80=9CWe believe the next step=
 forward will be the tokenization of financial assets.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0
The company that=E2=80=99s furthest along in making that happen, our portfo=
lio company Ondo Finance [ https://substack.com/redirect/437dfd08-e5ab-429e=
-aeee-440d94f71738?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-=
