One of the criticisms of fintech products is that they put lipstick on a pi=
g: they=E2=80=99re shiny interfaces on top of the same slow, antiquated sys=
tems the industry has relied on for decades. That=E2=80=99s not because fin=
tech companies don=E2=80=99t want to build better products, but because the=
