d&#8217;s Frank Hayes </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/fe364=
d81-c53c-4c5e-b142-8e8647d2c566?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjm=
