: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; l=
ine-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">&#8220;You drive on the BQE (Brookly=
n-Queens Expressway),&#8221; he said. &#8220;You know how bad decade-long p=
