g any one of them the wrong way might mean game over, so you have to go ver=
y slowly and very carefully, all while protecting the core.&#160;</span></p=
><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; ma=
rgin: 0 0 20px 0;">Jon Daplyn, who was responsible for these systems at Mor=
gan Stanley, echoed Chris&#8217; assessment and added a technical lens. To =
