4, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Goldman wa=
s the first to sell. Over the course of the day on March 26th, &#8220;Goldm=
an Sachs sold $10 billion of shares in stocks linked to Archegos.&#8221;&#1=
60;</p><blockquote style=3D"border-left: 4px solid #51b4e9; margin: 20px 0;=
