ings call. &#8220;We identified the risk early and took prompt action consi=
stent with the terms of our contract with the client.&#8221;</span></em></p=
></blockquote><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-hei=
ght: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Morgan Stanley was almost as quick, dumping=
 $8 billion that same day. The firm lost $911 million between money owed by=
