mura wasn&#8217;t as lucky. It lost $2.87 billion in the winddown.</p><p st=
yle=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: =
0 0 20px 0;"><span>But the biggest loser was Credit Suisse. The Swiss bank =
was the slowest to appreciate and unwind its exposure to Archegos, and lost=
