;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-heigh=
t: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">It wasn&#8217;t enough. Two years later, in M=
arch 2023, the Swiss Government and Swiss Financial Market Supervisory Auth=
ority organized the $3.2 billion fire sale of Credit Suisse to its Swiss Ri=
