;">7 Powers</a></em><span> as a framework, infrastructure has high </span><=
strong>switching costs</strong><span>. Once a customer has built their prod=
ucts and systems on top of your infrastructure, it&#8217;s expensive and ev=
en risky for them to switch to another system.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"=
color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20p=
x 0;">It cuts both ways. High switching costs are why banks still use the s=
