ng costs to work for itself.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-si=
ze: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Overcoming incumbents&#82=
17; switching costs is why Clear Street isn&#8217;t just building infrastru=
cture, but also products that run on top of it.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color:=
 rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">=
Buying a brokerage to prove the advantages of operating on Clear Street&#82=
